title: Welcome To Quantitative Chinese Economics History
text:
This is the first post in a Quantitative Chinese Economics History blog. Welcome!

I find that it is very effective for students to learn new economics theories when we have a concrete example. Therefore, I decided to collect some interesting examples from Chinese economics history since I am interested in Chinese history and many people many are interested in them as well.
